{"tid":2248672,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"白俄羅斯數萬人示威　據報約50人被捕","createTime":"2020-10-18T18:27:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-19T15:35:21.000Z","uid":227801,"like":25,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"8f31fb7ae14b743c8adb509c402202b79c7a754f","tid":2248672,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T18:27:25.000Z","msg":"香港冇咗影<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1555427-20201019.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1555427-20201019.htm&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1a02FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=2d9be3b5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1555427-20201019.htm&h=bff03b09\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1555427-20201019.htm</a><br />\n白俄羅斯反政府示威持續，大批民眾在首都明斯克上街，要求總統盧卡申科下台。<br />\n<br />\n國際文傳通訊社報道，超過3萬名示威者上街，大約50人被警方拘捕。報道又說，市內部分地區的流動網絡訊號受到干擾。<br />\n<br />\n示威民眾附近傳出類似震撼彈的聲響。警方高層早前警告，保留使用槍械對付示威者的權利。<br />\n<br />\n流亡立陶宛的反對派領袖季哈諾夫斯卡婭早前促請盧卡申科在本月25日前辭職，否則會發起全國大罷工。"},{"pid":"4fa23ac3f8d7460577d7aa70cb833158262b1630","tid":2248672,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T18:31:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4774b8069a289263af455854f386c7ff901447e0","tid":2248672,"uid":21545,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T18:51:27.000Z","msg":"超過3萬名示威者上街 一定運動已完啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8d6a3fdeb3f1499d35ca827d5e89e4f7045645c","tid":2248672,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"